      • closure

        @Nullable
ConceptMap closure​(@Nonnull
                   StringType name,
                   @Nonnull
                   List<Coding> concept)
        Invokes the "closure" operation against the ConceptMap resource.
        Parameters:
        name - the name that defines the particular context for the subsumption based closure table
        concept - concepts to add to the closure table
        Returns:
        a list of new entries (code / system --> code/system) that the client should add to its closure table. The only kind of entry mapping equivalences that can be returned are equal, specializes, subsumes and unmatched
        See Also:
        Operation $closure on ConceptMap
